<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3955943>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. A, B. Holotype male (dorsal, ventral) and C, D. Allotype female (dorsal, ventral) of Carminda surpresa sp. nov. Scale bar = 1 cm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3955943/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3955945>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Male genitalia of Carminda surpresa sp. nov. A. Lateral view; B. Dorsal view; C. Ventral view; D. Detailed ventral view of valvae tip and the small “teeth” at costa region; E. Aedeagus (lateral above, dorsal below); F. Magnified view of anterior portion of aedeagus showing details of randomly distributed knobs and the small cornuti; G, H. Female genitalia (lateral left, ventral right)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3955945/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3955947>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Immature stages of Carminda surpresa sp. nov. A. Freshly laid egg in lateral view; B. Egg in lateral view showing the beginning of larva development; C, D. First instar (dorsal, lateral); E, F. Second instar near molting (dorsal, ventral); G, H. Third instar (dorsal, lateral); I, J. Fourth (last) instar (dorsal, lateral); K, L, M. Pupa (ventral, lateral, dorsal)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3955947/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3955949>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Natural habitat and adults of Carminda surpresa sp. nov. A, B. General view of the wet grasslands where the species can be found; C. Adult male perched with wings closed on an inflorescence of Baccharis sp. (Asteraceae); D. Adult female perched on a grass leaf with wings opened." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3955949/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3955951>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Maximum likelihood tree obtained with RAxML showing the phylogenetic relationship of Carminda surpresa sp. nov. with other species of Carminda and with other sampled genera in Euptychiina subtribe. Number below branches are bootstrap values (values below 75 are not shown)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3955951/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

